%N A396558 Expansion of e.g.f. LambertW(-LambertW(LambertW(-x))).
%F A396558 a(n) ~ n^(n-1) * exp(n*exp(-1)) * LambertW(1) / (sqrt(1-exp(-1)) * (1 + LambertW(1))).
%F A396558 a(n) = Sum_{i,j,k >= 0 and i+j+k=n-1} ((n-1)!/(i!*j!*k!)) * n^i * (n-i)^j * (-(k+1))^k. - _Seiichi Manyama_, May 31 2026
